ai_summary.en: With Bitcoin's Fear & Greed Index at 'Extreme Fear' (20), the broader crypto market is highly cautious. Despite this, ETH whales show slight bullishness with positive stablecoin inflows and significant volume, suggesting smart money is cautiously accumulating. In stark contrast, SOL whales exhibit bearish sentiment with substantial stablecoin outflows and much lower volume, indicating retail capitulation. This divergence suggests continued pressure on speculative assets, while institutional interest might provide a floor for ETH in the near term.
ai_summary.zh: 比特币恐惧与贪婪指数处于‘极度恐惧’(20)，整个加密市场情绪非常谨慎。尽管如此，ETH鲸鱼表现出轻微看涨情绪，稳定币净流入量为正且交易量巨大，表明聪明资金正在谨慎积累。形成鲜明对比的是，SOL鲸鱼则呈现看跌情绪，稳定币大量流出且交易量显著降低，预示着散户投降。这种分化表明投机性资产将继续面临压力，而机构兴趣可能在短期内为ETH提供支撑。
